[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "そんな、みんな石化しちゃったなんて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00437",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "石化しない相棒たちが時間を稼いでるけど、\nどこまで持つかは正直分かんないよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_00438",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "今こうしている間にも戦ってるなんて。\n異邦人に援軍を求めに行く時間は……厳しいわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00439",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "こういうときのための光星隊なのに……っ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00440",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "とにかく、今は一分一秒も大事！\nすぐに石化を治すための薬を調合するよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00441",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "レシピは……レスナのアトリエに参考になりそうなのが\nあったはず。向こうになら、素材ももっとある",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00442",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "うん、できる。アタシに任せて！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00443",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "っしゃい、できた！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00444",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "早いな！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_037_00445",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "量もちょっとだけの、試薬ですから！\nこの方向性でいいのか、確認したい……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00446",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "失敗したときのことを考えて、服のとこらへんで……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00447",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "こいつは……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_037_00448",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "うん、上手くいった！　石化なんて初めてだったけど\nこの考え方で間違ってない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00449",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "これまで錬金術と真摯に向き合っていたから、\n緊急事態でも正解を導けたのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00450",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "本当に、調合の引き出しを増やしといてよかった……\nあとは素材の確保と時間との勝負！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00451",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "素材の確保は任せて。どんな魔物相手でも\n生き血が必要なら絞って持ってくる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00452",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "物騒ね！　でもそういうのは冒険者の十八番よ。\nぜひ私にも手伝わせてちょうだい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00453",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "そういえばあなたは……？\n話をうかがう限り、冒険者のようだが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_037_00454",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ええ、私は冒険者、メーヴェ・シュテルネンリヒト。\nレスナの母親でもあるわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00455",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "うちの娘を石像にしてくれた\n九偉人のヘルトとかいうの、絶ッッ対許せん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00456",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ええ、あいつには私も煮え湯を飲まされた……\nこの手でなんとしても一矢報いてやる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00457",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "アタシもあいつに目にもの見せてやりたいのは同じ！\nみんなで力を合わせてやったりましょ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00458",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ええ！　そこでアルビーナにちょっと相談があるの。\nヘルトへの対抗策を考えたんだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00459",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "んん？　なんでございましょ――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00460",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "えっ？　いや、無茶な……ただでさえ今は\n石化解除薬で手いっぱいなんすけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00461",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "その薬の素材集めは手伝ってあげるし、\nそっち優先でいいから、後で考えておいて！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00462",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "3986021654722714881",
		"text": "ええー……分かった、分かりました！\nなんとかしてみますから素材よろしくお願いします！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00463",
		"still_path_hash": "4227931788932007159",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]